<p>I absolutely love this one, and agree that it deserves to be 001, for the reasons you listed above. I actually just completed SCP-999 a few days ago (before reading this post), and it is in some small way the exact opposite of yours: Use SCP-999 enough, and gods are sealed off from the world, effectively dead.</p>

